snippet.title: Are Companies Cheating Us? | Dreamz Unlimited | Consumer Protection
snippet.description:
How Can a Customer Fight for Their Rights?
Every customer has the right to safety, information, choice, and redressal. But what can you do when these rights are violated? Here's how a customer can fight for their rights:
Know Your Rights - First, be aware of your basic consumer rights — such as the right to be informed, the right to choose, the right to safety, and the right to seek redressal.
Keep Proof - Always keep receipts, bills, warranty cards, emails, or any communication related to the product or service. These documents act as evidence if a complaint needs to be raised.
Talk to the Seller - In many cases, simply raising the issue with the shop or service provider politely can solve the problem.
File a Formal Complaint - If the seller refuses to help, you can file a complaint with: Department of Legal Metrology & Consumer Protection
(Respective States)
Use Social Media - Tagging companies on social platforms like Twitter or Instagram often gets their attention quickly. Many companies take online reputation seriously.
Take Legal Action - If needed, you can approach a consumer court. These courts are specially set up to handle consumer disputes in a quicker and more affordable manner.
This video is produced by
Department of Legal Metrology & Consumer Protection
Govt. of Nagaland

localized.title: Are Companies Cheating Us? | Dreamz Unlimited | Consumer Protection
localized.description:
How Can a Customer Fight for Their Rights?
Every customer has the right to safety, information, choice, and redressal. But what can you do when these rights are violated? Here's how a customer can fight for their rights:
Know Your Rights - First, be aware of your basic consumer rights — such as the right to be informed, the right to choose, the right to safety, and the right to seek redressal.
Keep Proof - Always keep receipts, bills, warranty cards, emails, or any communication related to the product or service. These documents act as evidence if a complaint needs to be raised.
Talk to the Seller - In many cases, simply raising the issue with the shop or service provider politely can solve the problem.
File a Formal Complaint - If the seller refuses to help, you can file a complaint with: Department of Legal Metrology & Consumer Protection
(Respective States)
Use Social Media - Tagging companies on social platforms like Twitter or Instagram often gets their attention quickly. Many companies take online reputation seriously.
Take Legal Action - If needed, you can approach a consumer court. These courts are specially set up to handle consumer disputes in a quicker and more affordable manner.
This video is produced by
Department of Legal Metrology & Consumer Protection
Govt. of Nagaland

snippet.description:
Presenting official audio of #AchurjyaBorpatra's #RongOiRongali  (#AssameseSong) exclusively on Achurjya Borpatra Official.

"ৰঙ ঐ ৰঙালী" 
কণ্ঠ : আচুৰ্য বৰপাত্ৰ 
কথা - সুৰ - সংগীত পৰিচালনা : শোণিত গগৈ, পংকজ বৰা 
শব্দ সংমিশ্ৰণ : দিগন্ত বৰদলৈ 
সহযোগী কণ্ঠ : জনম কাশ্যপ, ৰাগদীপ চেতিয়া 
বাদ্য শিল্পী : 
ঢোল : পংকজ বৰা,লাচিত বৰুৱা,অংকুৰ বুঢ়াগোহাঁই 
তাল-পেঁপা-গগণা-ধূতং :
পিটি বৰা 
বাঁহী : কৈলাশ ৰাভা 
বাণীবন্ধন কক্ষ : ষ্টুডিঅ' অ'ডিঅহলিক 
বাণীবদ্ধক : স্বপ্নিল দত্ত, নিখিলেশ বৰা 
বিশেষ কৃতজ্ঞতা : বিশাল মহন বৰা, অভিনন্দন বৰা, প্ৰাণজিত নাথ

snippet.title: क्यों हमे जीते जी मार डालना चाहती हैं Prem Granth Movie Scene - Madhuri - Sulbha Arya - Om Puri
snippet.description:
Prem Granth is a 1996 Hindi romantic bollywood drama film starring Rishi Kapoor, Madhuri Dixit, Anupam Kher and Om Puri. The story revolves around Somen, son a Hindu priest of the village. Somen falls in love with Kajri who belongs to a lower caste and Somen’s family disapprove their relationship. When Kajri goes missing, Somen leaves his village to stay with his uncle. Will the lovers ever reunite?

💎 Movie : Prem Granth - प्रेम ग्रन्थ (1996)
💎 Director: Rajiv Kapoor - राजीव कपूर 
💎 Cast: 
    Shammi Kapoor - शम्मी कपूर as Nandlal
    Rishi Kapoor - ऋषि कपूर as Somen
    Madhuri Dixit - माधुरी दीक्षित as Kajri
    Anupam Kher - अनुपम खेर as Swami Dharam Bhooshan
    Om Puri - ओम पूरी as Baliram
    Prem Chopra - प्रेम चोपड़ा as Kedar Nath
    Reema Lagoo - रीमा लागू as Parvati
    Himani Shivpuri as Natho
    Sulabha Arya as Laxmi
    Govind Namdeo as Roop Sahai
💎 Music : Laxmikant–Pyarelal - लक्ष्मीकांत - प्यारेलाल 


#rishikapoor #madhuri #shammikapoor #anupamkher #romantic #latest #90s #90severgreen

Maharaj dreams of a grand New Year celebration and plans something special for everyone. Will everything go as planned?

Show Name: Gopal Bhar - গোপালভাঁড়
Directed By: Sourav Mondal, Hansa Mondal
Written By: Hansa Mondal
Original language: Bengali
Episode No: 1143

#GopalBhar #sonyaath #গোপালভর 

About Gopal Bhar:
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him as a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.

snippet.title: Gokuldham के Gents को क्यों पहननी पड़ी साड़ी?| Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | 14 Apr 2025
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Jetha finds himself in a tricky situation one side is his wife and another side his best friend on whose victory he should be happy. Daya wins the arm wrestling and Jetha claps and appreciates her. Jetha and Sundar come face to face for arm wrestling and Jetha wins. All first-round winners go into the second round. Jetha and Champak face each other in arm wrestling and Champak wins. We see Komal and Goli one by one win overall contestants. In the end, Dr. Hathi and Popatlal come against each other for arm wrestling.


Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 632
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Click Here To Watch More Episodes Of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?
list=PLfyXOEyr93G3QQIKGExbP8b1NqpJKa_xb

snippet.title: Falguni Pathak - Aiyo Rama (Music Video) | Divya Khosla Kumar | Romantic Song
snippet.description:
Immerse yourself in the vibrant world of Gujarati folk music with #Revibe brings #AiyoRama a captivating song by the renowned #FalguniPathak from her 1998 album #MeriChunarUddUddJaye.

This energetic track is a celebration of love, longing, and the anticipation of meeting one's beloved.
Falguni Pathak's powerful and expressive vocals bring the emotions of the song to life. Her voice effortlessly conveys the mix of excitement, nervousness, and joy that one experiences when anticipating the arrival of their loved one.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Credits: 

Singer: Falguni Pathak
Music: Lalit Sen
Lyrics: Lalit Sen, Naqsh Layalpuri
Movie/Album: Meri Chunar Udd Udd Jaye
Label: Universal Music India
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Aiyo rama hath se ye dil kho gaya

Aiyo rama hath se ye dil kho gaya

snippet.title: Adventure | Stand-up Comedy by Ravi Gupta
snippet.description:
When life gives you lemons, sell them and go to the mountains.
You’ll come back with beautiful memories and a sore body.

This is a story about a trek I did with my friend.
I spend a lot of time in the mountains. There’s no place more peaceful.
But the moment I have to walk on uneven ground, everything changes. My body starts questioning my soul.
It’s tough, annoying, and sometimes painful.
But once I’m back home, all that’s left is a funny story—and now, that story will stay with all of us forever.

Hope you enjoyed the video.
Please like, comment & share it.

I’m also performing my stand-up comedy special in the UK and touring across India and internationally!
Tickets for all my shows are live here: https://linktr.ee/Shudhdesicomic

snippet.title: ஒரு கப் ரசம் போதும், வேற எதுவும் வேணாம்! Tomato Rasam This Tasty? Chef Deena's Kitchen
snippet.description:
Kalyana Veetu Rasam
Ready to unlock the secret to that irresistible wedding rasam? Chef Deena is on a mission, and he's teamed up with Chennai's very own young culinary whiz, Mr. Harish from Janani Catering Services in West Mambalam!  Get ready to learn the nuances of an aromatic and flavorful rasam recipe, a staple at South Indian weddings, as Mr. Harsh guides us through the step-by-step process. Let's dive in and discover the magic of Janani Catering's Kalyanam Rasam! 

Sri Janani Catering Service
Mr. Harish
Contact : 9840703703

கல்யாண வீட்டு ரசம் | Kalyaana Veettu Rasam (Wedding-Style Rasam)
Thakkali Rasam
Tomato - 1 Kg
Mustard - 1 Tsp
Cumin Seeds - 1 Tsp
Pepper - 35 g
Asafoetida - 1 Tsp
Tamarind - 100 g
Jaggerry - 1/2 Tsp
Chrushed Garlic - 100 g
Dry Red Chilli - 6 to 7 Nos 
Green Chilli - 6 to 7 Nos
Curry Leaves - As Required 
Coriander Leaves - As Required 
Turmeric Powder - 1/2 Tsp
Salt - To Taste 
Gingelly Oil - 200 ml 
Ghee - For Tempering
 


My Amazon Store { My Picks and Recommended Product }
https://www.amazon.in/shop/chefdeenaskitchen

_______________
Hello!!  My Name is chef Deena from the popular Adupangarai show in Jaya TV Viewers must have seen me in Zee Tamil shows as well.  My Culinary journey as a trainee to become an Executive Chef is incredible. My experience in the culinary field is for more than fifteen years and my USP is Indian cooking !! Apart from being a TV cookery host, my experience lies mainly with being employed in some of the major star hotels across the country especially the Marriott group.

     Chef Deena Cooks is my English Youtube Channel! Practical, simple recipes are my forte and using minimal easily available ingredients is my hallmark. Rudiments of cooking and baking are taught from scratch and any amateur cook can learn to make exciting dishes by watching my channel!  Also, Cooking traditional foods, Easy cooking Recipes, Healthy Snacks, Indian curries, gravies, Baking and Millions of other homemade treats. 

Subscribe to Chef Deena Cooks (CDK) for more cooking videos.

snippet.description:
A melody that will make your heart say, "Khudaya, Ishq, ho gaya." 
This one's all about #BringingLoveBack ❤️

👉 Subscribe to Saregama Music: https://bit.ly/3FkAS0W

Credits:
Song Name - Khudaya Ishq
Composer - Amit Trivedi
Singers - Arijit Singh and Shilpa Rao

A Richer Lens Entertainment presents in association with Aarjay Pictures
A Richer Lens and Indian Stories Production Presents Abir Gulaal
#bringingloveback

Starring Fawad Khan, Vaani Kapoor, Lisa Haydon, Riddhi Dogra, Farida Jalal, Soni Razdan, Parmeet Sethi, Rahul Vora, Amrit Sandhu, Sujoy De, Zorawar Singh Ahluwalia and Dev Agrawal 
Directed by Aarti S Bagdi 
Produced by Vivek B. Agrawal, Avantika Hari, Rakesh Sippy, Firuzi Khan
Co-Producer - Raza Namazi

Choreographer - Vijay Ganguly
(London) Choreography - Rohan Shah & Shruti Shah
Cinematographer - Tribhuvan Babu Sadineni
Production Designer - Sunil Nigvekar

Lyrics:

Mukhda:
Lakh sitaron ki ek thi dua
Dil pe tabhi to zor na chala

Khudaya ishq re ishq re ishq re
Khudaya ishq hote hote ho gaya

Khudaya ishq re ishq re ishq re
Khudaya ishq hote hote ho gaya

Main to loon sab saansein ab tere naam ki
Ik tu hi bas mera dunia kis kaam ki

Chadhe hain tere rang
Ke ab tere sang
Ye laage mann mera jogiya
Khudaya ishq hote hote ho gaya..

Khudaya ishq re ishq re ishq re
Khudaya ishq hote hote ho gaya

Antara:
Tere meri ishq kahani
Jaise dariya ka behta paani

Samjhega na koi
Hai ye baat ruhaani

Mere dil ke lafz churake
Kehti hai nazar deewani

Ik tu naya naya sa
Aur dunia lage puraani

Saari taarikhon pe haq hai tera
Aur kya chahun tu hai mera

Khudaya ishq re ishq re ishq re
Khudaya ishq hote hote ho gaya

Main to loon sab saansein ab tere naam ki
Ik tu hi bas mera dunia kis kaam ki

Chadhe hain tere rang
Ke ab tere sang
Ye laage mann mera jogiya
Khudaya ishq hote hote ho gaya

Khudaya ishq re ishq re ishq re

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 4371 | 14 Apr 2025 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4371: Bapuji’s Race Against Time
--------------------------------------------------------

snippet.title: என்னுடைய தம்பிக்கு நிச்சயதார்த்தம் / புது பொன்னுமாப்பிளையை பார்க்கலாம் வாங்க / Engagement function,
snippet.description:
#Engagementfunction

என்னுடைய தம்பிக்கு நிச்சயதார்த்தம் / புது பொன்னுமாப்பிளையை பார்க்கலாம் வாங்க / Engagement function 

#wetting 
#weddingphotography 
#villageEngagement
#simplevillageEngagemen
#Engagement 

#engagementvideo 

#engagementvideotamil
#engagementvideodance

வணக்கம் நண்பர்களே 🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏  
தங்கள் இல்லங்களில் நடைபெறும் அனைத்து விசேஷங்களுக்கும், பிறந்த நாள்,திருமண நாள் திருமண நாள்  நினைவு நாள் மற்றும் இதர விசேஷங்களுக்கும் நீங்கள் எங்கள் மூலமாக சிரமப்படும் மக்களுக்கு உணவு ,உணவு பொருள்கள் ,மற்றும் வீடு இல்லாதவர்களுக்கு வீடு கட்டி கொடுக்க மற்றும் கணவரை இழந்து வருமானம் இன்றி  வாடும் பெண்களுக்கு அவர்களின் வாழ்வாதாரத்திற்கு அவர்களுக்கு ,ஆடு,மாடு, பெட்டிக்கடை,தையல் இயந்திரம் ,மாவு அரைக்கும் இயந்திரம் மற்றும் ஊனமுற்றவர்களுக்கு உதவிகள் ,குழந்தைகளின் படிப்பு செலவுகளுக்கு மற்றும் இன்னும் நிறைய உதவிகள் எங்கள்   My Country Foods சேனல் மூலமாக நீங்கள் செய்ய விரும்பினால்  இந்த மெயில் IDக்கு மெயில் அனுப்பவும்   anandhaeswari4@gmail.com நாங்கள் உங்களை விரைவில் தொடர்பு கொள்வோம்

snippet.description:
Gokuldham Society | Gada Electronics | Bonus | Financial Year

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. Are you ready for the challenge? 

 Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  #GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame


Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

Produced By: Neela Asit Modi, Asit Kumarr Modi

snippet.title: राजस्थानी दाल ढोकली-जब कुकिंग का मन न हो तब बनायें-स्वादिष्ट व ईजी One-Pot Wholesome Meal Dal Dhokli
snippet.description:
पारंपरिक खाना-दाल में पकी नरम ढोकली-फटाफट वआसान- एक बर्तन में तैयार संपूर्ण भोजन,  Grandma’s Rajasthani Dal Dhokli Recipe – Pure Nostalgia, Spicy, Tangy, and Delicious – This Dal Dhokli Has It All

#daldhokli #onepotmeal #indianrecipe 

Ingredients for Rajasthani Dal Dhokla
अरहर दाल - Arhar dal - 1 cup (200 grams)
नमक - Salt - 1 tsp
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
टमाटर - Tomato - 2 no
गेहूं का आटा - Wheat flour - 1 cup
बेसन - Gram flour - 1/4 cup
नमक - Salt - 1/4 tsp
अजवाइन - Carom seeds - 1/4 tsp
लाल मिर्च पाउडर - Red chilli powder - 1/4 tsp
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
अदरक मिर्च पेस्ट - Ginger chilli paste - 1/2 tsp
हरा धनिया - Coriander - 1 tsp
घी - Ghee - 2 tbsp

For Tadka
घी - Ghee - 2-3 tbsp
जीरा - Cumin seeds - 1/2 tsp
हींग - Asafoetida - 1 pinch
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander powder - 1 tsp
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1 tsp, chopped
अदरक - Ginger - 1 tsp, grated
कश्मीरी लाल मिर्च - Kashmiri red chilli - 1 tsp
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli - 1/4 tsp, crushed
नमक - Salt - 1/2 tsp
अमचूर पाउडर - Dry mango powder - 1/2 tsp
गरम मसाला - Garam masala - 1/2 tsp
हरा धनिया - Coriander

snippet.title: தமிழ் வருடப் பிறப்பு 2025 | விசுவாவசு ஆண்டிற்கான வழிபாடு, நேரம் & முறை | கனி காணுதல்| Tamil New year
snippet.description:
#tamilnewyear2025 #தமிழ்ப்புத்தாண்டு #தமிழ்வருடப்பிறப்பு
#தமிழ்ப்புத்தாண்டு #தமிழ்வருடப்பிறப்பு 

சித்திரை மாதத்தில் பிறந்தவர்களும், குழந்தை பெற்றவர்களும் பார்க்க வேண்டிய பதிவு | Desa Mangayarkarasi
https://youtu.be/XxAB_XVBMZo

மருத்து நீராடி தமிழ்ப் புத்தாண்டை வரவேற்று வழிபடும் முறை | கனி காணுதல் | தமிழ் வருட பிறப்பு
https://youtu.be/0g00MJwEQNw

செல்வம், ஆரோக்கியம், நீண்ட ஆயுள் பெற தமிழ்ப் புத்தாண்டை வரவேற்று வழிபடும் முறை.   மேலும் கனி காணுதல், அறுசுவை உணவு படைத்தல், வழிபடும் நேரம் என பல தகவல்களை திருமதி. தேச மங்கையர்க்கரசி அம்மா அவர்கள் அளித்துள்ளார். 

- ஆத்ம ஞான மையம்

snippet.title: श्री हनुमान जन्मोत्सव | Shree Hanuman Janmotsav | Dr Kumar Vishwas
snippet.description:
मनोजवं मारुततुल्यवेगं, जितेन्द्रियं बुद्धिमतां वरिष्ठम्। वातात्मजं वानरयूथमुख्यं, श्रीरामदूतं शरणं प्रपद्ये॥
आप सबको शक्ति और शालीनता के एकल पर्याय, विद्या के सर्वश्रेष्ठ प्रतीक, बजरंग बली महावीर हनुमान जन्मोत्सव की पूर्व संध्या पर ढेर सारी शुभकामनाएँ! 🙏🏻💐इस पुण्य-अवसर पर अपने-अपने राम ऊर्जा-सत्र का यह विशेष प्रसंग आप सबकी आस्था को सादर समर्पित है। 😍🙏🏻
#kumarvishwas #hanumanjanmotsav #apneapneram 

Follow us on :- 

YouTube :- http://youtube.com/KumarVishwas
Facebook :- https://www.facebook.com/KumarVishwas
Twitter :- https://twitter.com/DrKumarVishwas
Instagram :- https://www.instagram.com/KumarVishwas

Subscribe To Our Other YouTube Channels:-

Apne Apne Ram    : https://www.youtube.com/@ApneApneRamOfficial
  
The KV Studio        : https://www.youtube.com/@TheKVStudio

Apne Apne Shyam : https://www.youtube.com/@ApneApneShyamOfficial

-------------------------------------------------------------------
About Dr Kumar Vishwas :

The people who make history are the ones who not only give their life to their career but also give their career a new life. When the career is that of a poet, every step is a risk. Kumar Vishwas is one such poet who has gifted himself an era of such a popularity which other poets cant’t even dream of.
Kumar Vishwas is a poet who went beyond the stereotypical norms of ‘Kavi Sammelan’ or poetic functions and made it a performer’s stage. He has mastered and excelled in all aspects in whatever he has done. Dr Kumar Vishwas has been doing this since years just with a mic and his poems and wits in his soulful voice.
His popularity can be guessed by the fact that the audience sings his verses with him, he has crafted a new dimension by rejuvenating the structure and mechanics of Hindi poetry and Kavi Sammelan.
 
Recently, Dr. Kumar Vishwas has started hosting energy sessions popularly Known as Apne Apne Ram and Apne Apne Shyam where he talks about life skills of Shri Ram’s and Shri Krishna's life, and the applicability of the same in one’s own life to over come the challenges and social concerns we come across in our life.

Mann Mast Malang Episode 25 Teaser - 13th April 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Mann Mast Malang is a love story that traces the journey of two families who, once close and united by their children's engagement, become sworn enemies due to a single incident. As the story unfolds, Kabeer and Riya, former fiancés turned enemies, start to grow closer and eventually fall in love. Their love story faces the challenge of uniting their feuding families, as they strive to make their love successful against all odds.

snippet.title: Get Ready For WAR | By Sandeep Maheshwari
snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

Lyrics In Hindi - 

डोल कुएंमलटके 
तनेदेखन खातर लागी भीड़ या भार पनघट पे,, 
र पोर पोर मटके यो डोल कुएंमलटके,, 
तूआती जाती नेछेड़ेतनेसब लागेसेहटके,, 
या बठै ेजहाज के मगोर रामराम रटके,,
ना मओढ़ना सगं वा उ मेरा पला लटके 

 तरेेढुंगेचोट,, 
या उमर हैछोट,, सर पेटोकनी भार है,,  
मेरेबाल येसि क,, पाटेकि लक,, 
मनेगाल chuni तार है,,  
येआखं तरे जनू ो आर है,, 
मजमा padra सुकटके,,,

र पोर पोर मटके यो डोल कुएंमलटके,,  
तरे टूटेपायल,, करगी घायल,,
बठै कुण मचांद रोवे  मेर आखं मकाजल,, 
बरसेबादल ,,बि न मोसन बरसात हो  -
योगी अमरजीत य तरे आखं या मखटके , 
र पोर पोर मटके यो डोल कुएंमलटके,,

Lyrics In English - 

tane  dekhan khatar lagi bheed ya bhari panghat pe ,,
pori pori matke dhol kue main latke,,
tu aati jaati ne chede raha kr hatke ,,
Jhaaj ke main beth gori raam ratke,,
Na main odhna sangwau mera palla latke,,

tere dhunge choti umar ya choti sar pe tokni bhari se,,
merw baal h silki patti kilki gaal main chunni tari se,,,
aankh meri ye aari tu padjaga katke,,,
jhaaj ke main beth gori Raam Ratke,,

Teri khanke payal kargi ghayal beth kun main chand rove ,,,
meri aankh main kajal barse badal bin mosam barsat hove,,,
yogi Amarjeet kyu teri aankhya main khatke,,,

es.title: ¿EL PRIMER EVENTO DE LA COMUNIDAD P2W?

Episode 4370: Bapuji’s Race Against Time
--------------------------------------------------------
With time running out, Bapuji hopes to catch up with Mannu before his flight to America. An unexpected detour slows him down as he looks for a way to reach in time.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:

Dayan Episode 15 - [Eng Sub] - Mehwish Hayat - Ahsan Khan - Hira Mani - 14th April 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Dayan is a gripping story of a girl fighting for justice after enduring a series of injustices. It follows Nihaal, a young woman whose life is shattered by a tragic turn of events.
The events that follow shake Nihaal to her core, drastically altering her personality. This leads Nihaal to embark on a journey to bring those responsible for ruining her life to justice.
Can Nihaal get the justice she deserves? Is Nihaal strong enough to take down the ones who wronged her? Can Nihaal handle everything life throws at her?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Writers: Fatima Faizan & Amber Azhar

Cast:
Mehwish Hayat as Nihaal/Misha
Ahsan Khan as Zawar Shah

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS! De Bruyne inspires stunning five-star City fightback! | Man City 5-2 Crystal Palace
snippet.description:
A Kevin De Bruyne-inspired City staged a stunning comeback from 2-0 down to overwhelm Crystal Palace 5-2 at the Etihad and so step up our charge for a Champions League place.

In what was a remarkable, incident-packed game, the Eagles had soared into an early two-goal lead through Eberechi Eze and Chris Richards and saw a potential third by Eze ruled out by VAR for offside.

But, in his first appearance at the Etihad since confirmation that he is to leave City this summer after 10 glorious years, skipper De Bruyne helped spark a quite magnificent comeback.

The Belgian first narrowed the deficit with a trademark first half free-kick before then being involved in Omar Marmoush’s leveller before the break.

De Bruyne it was who then set up Mateo Kovacic a minute after the restart to fire City ahead before James McAtee – on his first Premier League start for City – extended the advantage via a stunning Ederson assist.

Nico O’Reilly then got in on the scoring, registering his first Premier League goal to set the seal on what was a result to remember.

The victory moved Pep Guardiola’s side back up into fourth place in the Premier League table with six games of the season remaining.

snippet.title: Jaat Movie REVIEW | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
Jaat Movie Review By Deeksha Sharma. Jaat Featuring Sunny Deol vs Randeep Hooda in a Mass Masala Action Thriller based on a Layered Storytelling inspired from Mythology History of Raavan & his end by a Single Warrior! 

Jaat Full Movie Story Outline & Positives Negatives would be shared in this Video. Can Sunny Deol repeat Gadar 2 Success or Bollywood Formula with South Director prove unlucky just like Sikandar? Find out now!

Jaat is a 2025 Indian Hindi-language action thriller film written and directed by Gopichand Malineni (in his Hindi debut), and produced by Mythri Movie Makers and People Media Factory.The film stars Sunny Deol in lead role alongside Randeep Hooda, Vineet Kumar Singh, Regina Cassandra, Saiyami Kher, Ramya Krishnan, Jagapathi Babu and others in supporting roles. The film score and soundtrack is composed by Thaman S.

Principal photography commenced in June 2024 and was extensively filmed across Hyderabad, Bapatla and Visakhapatnam.

Jaat was theatrically released on 10 April 2025.

localized.title: Jaat Movie REVIEW | Deeksha Sharma
localized.description:
Jaat Movie Review By Deeksha Sharma. Jaat Featuring Sunny Deol vs Randeep Hooda in a Mass Masala Action Thriller based on a Layered Storytelling inspired from Mythology History of Raavan & his end by a Single Warrior! 

Jaat Full Movie Story Outline & Positives Negatives would be shared in this Video. Can Sunny Deol repeat Gadar 2 Success or Bollywood Formula with South Director prove unlucky just like Sikandar? Find out now!

Jaat is a 2025 Indian Hindi-language action thriller film written and directed by Gopichand Malineni (in his Hindi debut), and produced by Mythri Movie Makers and People Media Factory.The film stars Sunny Deol in lead role alongside Randeep Hooda, Vineet Kumar Singh, Regina Cassandra, Saiyami Kher, Ramya Krishnan, Jagapathi Babu and others in supporting roles. The film score and soundtrack is composed by Thaman S.

Principal photography commenced in June 2024 and was extensively filmed across Hyderabad, Bapatla and Visakhapatnam.

Jaat was theatrically released on 10 April 2025.
